name: Diário 1 - CWB (3/10)
description:
Fragment number 3 of "Diário 1 - CWB".

The third of 10 images that when put together, side by side, form a big panel. Think of the whole piece as an album, and each fragment as a song ;)

It's a visual diary that takes you on a walk through a city called Curitiba, in the south of Brasil. Memories of summer days spent smoking joints and wandering around.
